      "role": "user",
      "content": "the house is so quiet today. i keep walking into the kitchen thinking he's about to walk through the door or ask me where the coffee is... and then it hits me all over again. it feels like i'm just a ghost living in a museum of our life together. i don't even know why i bother waking up just to sit in this silence.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
